East 28th Street, west side, midway between Quentin Road and Ave. R. In the 1929 atlas it would be Ryder Ave., east side, between Quentin Road and Ave. R. B. Ryder (1857) and E.H. Ryder (1873) were the owners. This house was still standing in 1929. Ryder Ave., (Ryder Lane) does not exist on the
1935 Atlas of Brooklyn.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
